  <div class="container">
    <header class="section__header">
      <h2 class="h2">Proprietary Technology Overview</h2>
      <p class="subtle">A concise, high-level look at how the platform works under the hood.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- AI Technology -->
    <section aria-labelledby="ai-tech-title" class="block block--ai">
      <h3 id="ai-tech-title" class="h3">AI Technology</h3>
      <ul class="list list--bulleted">
        <li><strong>Avitate AI Engine:</strong> Orchestrates intake analysis, routing, and escalation logic using domain-tuned models.</li>
        <li><strong>Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG):</strong> Responses are grounded against vetted sources before output to reduce hallucinations.</li>
        <li><strong>Adaptive Intake:</strong> Dynamically adjusts follow-up questions based on user context, prior inputs, and detection of missing facts.</li>
        <li><strong>Multilingual:</strong> Supports multi-language intake and summaries with automatic language identification.</li>
        <li><strong>Document Automation:</strong> Generates structured summaries and draft documents for human review.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Security -->
    <section aria-labelledby="security-title" class="block block--security">
      <h3 id="security-title" class="h3">Security</h3>
      <ul class="list list--bulleted">
        <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Edge DDoS protection, WAF, and TLS termination.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Cloud:</strong> Hardened runtime, secret management, private networking, and audit logging.</li>
        <li><strong>Data Handling:</strong> PII minimized; encryption in transit and at rest; scoped access policies.</li>
        <li><strong>Operational Controls:</strong> Versioned deployments, rollout guards, and continuous monitoring.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section aria-labelledby="features-title" class="block block--features">
      <h3 id="features-title" class="h3">Key Features</h3>
      <ul class="grid grid--cards">
        <li class="card">
          <h4 class="card__title">Single Intake</h4>
          <p class="card__body">Collect once, reuse everywhere. Users avoid repeating themselves across forms and calls.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="card">
          <h4 class="card__title">Intelligent Distribution</h4>
          <p class="card__body">Routes cases to appropriate teams/partners based on rules, capacity, and specialization.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="card">
          <h4 class="card__title">Human Escalation</h4>
          <p class="card__body">Seamless handoff to people when risk, ambiguity, or urgency is detected.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="card">
          <h4 class="card__title">Efficiency & Tracking</h4>
          <p class="card__body">Analytics on conversion, time-to-resolution, and drop-off to improve operations.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section aria-labelledby="how-title" class="block block--how">
      <h3 id="how-title" class="h3">How It Works</h3>
      <ol class="steps">
        <li><strong>Intake:</strong> User submits text/voice; basic validation and consent checks run.</li>
        <li><strong>AI Processing:</strong> Avitate parses facts, normalizes entities, and detects missing info.</li>
        <li><strong>Grounding (RAG):</strong> System retrieves trusted materials to verify/anchor responses.</li>
        <li><strong>Distribution:</strong> Cases are scored and routed to the right destination.</li>
        <li><strong>Human Review:</strong> Staff can edit AI drafts, finalize, and notify the user.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <!-- Platform Capabilities -->
    <section aria-labelledby="capabilities-title" class="block block--capabilities">
      <h3 id="capabilities-title" class="h3">Platform Capabilities</h3>
      <ul class="list list--bulleted">
        <li><strong>Conversational AI:</strong> Clarifies facts and reduces friction in complex intakes.</li>
        <li><strong>Multimodal:</strong> Accepts documents, audio, and structured forms.</li>
        <li><strong>Integrations:</strong> Sheets/Drive for exports; webhooks for CRMs; optional email/SMS updates.</li>
        <li><strong>Auditability:</strong> Versioned prompts, retrieval logs, and action trails.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ (collapsible) -->
    <section aria-labelledby="faq-title" class="block block--faq">
      <h3 id="faq-title" class="h3">FAQ</h3>

      <details>
        <summary><strong>What makes this “proprietary”?</strong></summary>
        <div class="answer">
          Our orchestration logic, scoring models, routing heuristics, and prompt+retrieval tuning are customized for our use-case and data flows.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary><strong>Does AI output go straight to customers?</strong></summary>
        <div class="answer">
          No. High-impact outputs pass through safeguards and are available for human review, with measured rollout.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary><strong>Can partners integrate directly?</strong></summary>
        <div class="answer">
          Yes. We support webhooks and structured exports; additional connectors can be added on request.
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>

